# Scraper outputs, geocode caches, dedup reports, and other regenerable
# artifacts. Anchored with a leading `/` so the rules apply only to repo root,
# not to any equivalently-named files nested under src/, scripts/, etc.
/*-scrape.json
/*-cache.json
/dedup-*.json
/*-report.json
/*-audit.json
/scrape-result.json
/tasteatlas-*.json

# Screenshots and reference images dropped at the repo root. Keeps
